                            <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-item faq-item mb-3 border rounded">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                                            How do I buy an insurance policy?
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            Buying insurance on Policy Bazar is simple. Browse through our range of policies, compare features and prices, select the one that suits your needs, and click "Buy Now". You'll need to fill in some basic details, after which you can make the payment online. Your policy will be emailed to you within minutes.
                                        </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion-item faq-item mb-3 border rounded">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                                            How can I renew my policy?
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            You can renew your policy by logging into your Policy Bazar account, navigating to "My Policies", and clicking the "Renew" button on the policy you wish to renew. Alternatively, you can call us at 1800-123-4567 or visit your nearest branch for renewal assistance.
                                        </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion-item faq-item mb-3 border rounded">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                                            What documents are required for claim settlement?
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            The required documents vary by type of insurance. Generally, you need your policy document, ID proof, and claim form along with incident-specific documents like medical reports (for health claims), FIR (for motor claims), etc. Visit our Claims page for a detailed checklist.
                                        </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion-item faq-item mb-3 border rounded">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                                            How long does claim settlement take?
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            We strive to settle all claims within 7 working days of receiving complete documentation. Simple claims are often settled within 3-5 days. Complex claims may take up to 15 days. You can track your claim status online 24/7.
                                        </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion-item faq-item mb-3 border rounded">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">
                                            Can I cancel my policy?
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="faq5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            Yes, you can cancel your policy within the free-look period (15 days from policy issuance) for a full refund, provided no claim has been made. After the free-look period, cancellation will be subject to the terms and conditions mentioned in your policy document.
                                        </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="accordion-item faq-item mb-3 border rounded">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq6">
                                            How can I download my policy document?
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="faq6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            Log in to your Policy Bazar account, go to "My Policies", and click on the policy you want. You'll find a "Download Policy Document" button on the policy details page. The PDF will be downloaded instantly.
                                        </div>
                                </div>
